content:
Monitor the Entitlement Process Queue

When Salesforce triggers an entitlement process with time-dependent milestone actions, use the entitlement process queue to view pending actions and cancel them if necessary.

Available in: Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions with the Service Cloud. Entitlement process monitoring is not available in Professional Edition orgs.

User Permissions Needed:
To manage the entitlement process queue: Modify All Data
To view pending actions:
  - Search for active workflow rules or set filter criteria (Entitlement Process Name, Case Number, Milestone Name, Evaluation Date, Created Date, Username)
  - Select and cancel pending actions by clicking Delete.
title: Service Cloud Entitlement Process Queue
